# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════
# Whitelist-based .gitignore
# Default exclude all -> allow OSS public release targets only
# ══════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Step 1: Exclude all
*

# Step 2: Allow directory discovery (contents allowed individually)
!*/

# Step 3: Allow OSS public release target files
!.gitignore
!.gitattributes
!.gitleaks.toml
!CLAUDE.md
!LICENSE
!README.md
!README_ja.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!CONTRIBUTING.md
!SECURITY.md

# Claude Code settings (spinner verbs only, no secrets)
!.claude/
!.claude/settings.json

